  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a collection of short and experimental horror experiences, focused on surreal and bizarre plots, always maintaining Puko's style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FEATURES: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Anthology with 6 different games</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Each game contains a different horror story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Unlock trophies upon finishing each diskette</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Dialogues with different choices</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Inspired by classics like Tales from the Crypt and The Twilight Zone</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120250/extras/b6c03398f408478eab79c125bfa0203a.poster.avif?t=1765393931\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120250/extras/b6c03398f408478eab79c125bfa0203a.webm?t=1765393931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120250/extras/b6c03398f408478eab79c125bfa0203a.mp4?t=1765393931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120250/extras/ee50ef883619e5ac13feae88f0940c5d.poster.avif?t=1765393931\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120250/extras/ee50ef883619e5ac13feae88f0940c5d.webm?t=1765393931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120250/extras/ee50ef883619e5ac13feae88f0940c5d.mp4?t=1765393931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_c